701342f-a.title: Bronx: Jerome Avenue - 190th Street (West)
701342f-a.text:
Jerome Ave., west side, north from (No. 2553) but not including West 190th Street. The 5-story building is at the N.W. corner of West 192nd Street and on the right is the elevated structure of the I.R.T.
Woodlawan subway line.
January 30, 1938.
P. L. Sperr.
